general.gigTitle: develop a website and web app in react js

sellerCard.oneLiner: Worked at Samsung and Xerox as a software engineer
sellerCard.description: I am a software engineer who worked at Xerox and Samsung for a year each as a developer. I have completed tons of different software-related projects ranging from desktop app development, web development to smartphone app development. I have developed chatbots, web-based business applications, servers and cross-platform smartphone apps such as a diet planner and a virtual assistant for diabetics. I have gone into great depths in the aforementioned areas and can certainly help people in developing cool projects efficiently.

description.content:
I will develop your website/web app from scratch (no templates) using React js which is a leading industry-standard technology


I will develop it from scratch to end and will liaise with you at every stage to make sure that the website meets your requirements. Having worked for 6+ years of in React js, I have developed all sorts of projects ranging from social media, e-commerce to complex ERP systems


Please contact me first before placing the order so that the requirements can be understood better and ensure that we both are on the same page before embarking on a journey together

reviews.comment:
Working with Balawal was the most terrible, time-wasting and utterly useless job I have ever had the chance of trying to get done. His excuses and delays have caused my project a severe setback which I am not happy about at all however the audacity this individual has to screw up my project and then show me an aggressive tone is astonishing. At the end when his mistakes were put in front of his face, he said "I have better projects to be working on than this" anyone looking for front end work please beware of this scammer as he does not even have a real team and is not a valid agency even on Fiverr. Extremely rude and despicable person. 
LAST BUT NOT THE LEAST HE TOOK 5 MONTHS JUST TO ASK QUESTIONS AND THEN EVENTUALLY CANCELED THE ORDER !!!
Amazing work! I will be working with him more on various projects. Amazing work

Balawal has been fantastic to work with.

He took my vision for the web app and brought it to life with precision and creativity. He simply went above and beyond.

His and his team's technical expertise is evident in every aspect of the project, and he was always quick to address any questions or requests I had along the way (there were many).

The app is functional, well-designed, and exactly what I needed.

Again, Balawal truly goes above and beyond to ensure customer satisfaction, and I’m incredibly pleased with the outcome.

I highly recommend him for any web development project and will certainly be reaching out for further assistance in the future.

Working with Balawal and his team has been an absolute pleasure.

From the very beginning, he demonstrated a deep understanding of my project requirements and delivered a web app that exceeded my expectations.

Communication was clear and timely, and he was always open to feedback, making adjustments quickly and professionally without any hesitation.

The final product is not only as agreed but he went above and beyond.

If you're looking for a skilled, reliable web app developer, I highly recommend Balawal and his team!
